Package: dolpai-player
Version: 1.0.0
Section: video
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10),
         python3-pyqt6 (>= 6.4),
         python3-pyqt6.qtsvg,
         python3-vlc,
         vlc,
         ffmpeg,
         libxcb-cursor0
Recommends: libxcb-xinerama0
Maintainer: Dolpaii <https://github.com/Dolpaii>
Homepage: https://github.com/Dolpaii/dolpai-player
Description: Futuristic cyberpunk video player powered by VLC
 Dolpai Player is a premium video player for Linux with a cyberpunk-inspired
 dark UI featuring neon cyan and blue glow accents.
 .
 Built with Python, PyQt6, and the VLC media engine for broad format support.
 Supports MP4, MKV, AVI, MOV, WebM, FLV, TS and many more formats.
 .
 Features drag and drop, subtitle support, recent videos sidebar,
 fullscreen with auto-hide controls, and full keyboard shortcuts.
